This file contains the general installation hints to start using MiXiM. Any platform specific hints can be found in the various INSTALL.platform files.

Requirements
------------
- OMNeT++, at least version 3.2, downloadable at www.omnetpp.org
- make (or nmake)
- C++ compiler


Compiling
------------
Run ./mkmk (or ~.mac/cmd) to create all the makefiles. You may need to edit a few things (e.g. the omnet path for windows) in the mkmk (or ~.mac/cmd) file.

